Package: python3-dockgen
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Docker Compose and devcontainer generator for ROS and general development
 dockgen is a CLI tool that generates Docker Compose files and devcontainer
 configurations for ROS and general development environments. It provides an
 interactive wizard to configure GPU passthrough, display forwarding, network
 settings, volumes, and more.
